name: Cell 2187 (V)
Lore: '''Aren''t you a little short for a stormtrooper?''',
Text: 'Deploy on table. Once per game, may deploy spy R2-D2 (for free) on table from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. During your control phase, if R2-D2 is with captive Leia, may use 1 Force to release her.
